about = Page.find_or_initialize_by_permalink(permalink: 'about')
about.update_attributes!(
  document_code: '',
  name: 'About',
  content: %Q{
### THE CHALLENGE

The concept for Impact My Team came to being during a discussion on how best to help organisations fund products that are often over looked in Athletic Departments. The Athletic Training Room is the nucleus of any sports program yet one of the last recipients of funding.  Impact My Team was created to help change that paradigm by putting the power of crowdfunding to work for any institution.

### SOLUTION

iMPACT MY TEAM provides a simple tool for organizations to raise funds to equip their facilities with the latest equipment by engaging their community of supporters: including boosters, alumni, parents and corporate partners.   iMPACT MY TEAM will help Athletic Directors, Athletic Trainers, Coaches and Boosters set up their own fundraising campaigns to afford the equipment their athletes deserve.
  }
)

